data.description: SUPER BUY! Welcome to Bold River! Immaculately clean w/great curb appeal & is and ready for new owners. Embrace family living in this 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem in this popular Tomball neighborhood. Built in 2008, it offers roomy comfort, great interior light, gas-log fireplace, jetted soaker tub in the primary, gas cooking, & a versatile upstairs game room, &  a fenced yard with oversized patio and full sprinkler system. Laminate and tile flooring add elegance and ease of maintenance to the entire home. Washer, dryer, & 2 fridges are included! The Northern Point community features a park, playground, walking trails, & splash pad. When you're ready for shopping or commuting, everything you need is close at hand. From grocery stores to boutiques and eateries, convenience is at your doorstep. This fantastic property offers everything you desire at a price that's too good to pass up. Low HOA fees. Experience suburban living at its finest, complete with excellent schools and abundant amenities.
